{"tid":2051312,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"10屋苑二手估價齊升 半月最多漲4%","createTime":"2020-06-04T16:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T05:11:45.000Z","uid":175194,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6f0e8e9c9d55dc775a5cc5004d097c5a7635df","tid":2051312,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"設立港區國安法對樓市未見有大影響，銀行對二手樓市仍具信心，本報追蹤10個私人屋苑估價變化，多個屋苑的估價均較5月中時有所上升，最大升幅約4%，當中以九龍區的屋苑表現最佳。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情自4月中開始放緩，二手購買力釋放，樓市成交急增，部分屋苑連續兩個月出現量價齊升局面。由於氣氛暢旺，買家入市意慾高漲，及至5月下旬港區國安法設立，近兩個星期樓市所受影響不大。連帶銀行估價亦有上升趨勢，本報追蹤10個私人屋苑5月中及近日滙豐與中銀 網上估價走勢，發現大部分有所調升，最大升幅達4%，當中九龍區屋苑多個單位均有上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2661230/10%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E4%BC%B0%E5%83%B9%E9%BD%8A%E5%8D%87%20%E5%8D%8A%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E6%BC%B24%25?mtc=60011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2661230%2F10%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%258B%2591%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%25BD%258A%25E5%258D%2587%2520%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25BC%25B24%2525%3Fmtc%3D60011&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=c0e541d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2661230/10%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E4%BC%B0%E5%83%B9%E9%BD%8A%E5%8D%87%20%E5%8D%8A%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E6%BC%B24%25?mtc=60011</a>"},{"pid":"a4c94b84cc2dc9c5bdacdb628cbfdf1e0d021f63","tid":2051312,"uid":199670,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"二手樓頻蝕讓10宗,最大額損手820萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2051210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2051210</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隔離呢個post呃左好多人 以為樓價真係跌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig